  <h1>Welcome to <b>Green Farms Catering</b></h1>

  <p>At <u>Green Farms Catering</u>, our mission is to bring people together through food that is safe, inclusive, and <i>delicious</i>. We specialize in allergen-friendly catering for groups of all sizes, ensuring that everyone — regardless of dietary needs — can enjoy the meal.</p>

  <p class="red-text">We believe food should never separate people. That’s why our chefs work carefully with allergen-free ingredients.</p>
  <p class="blue-text">Gluten-free, dairy-free, nut-free, vegan — we design custom menus that fit your event.</p>

